<sup>[1]</sup>**.NET Framework 4 and .NET Framework 4 Client Profile affected.** The .NET Framework version 4 redistributable packages are available in two profiles: .NET Framework 4 and .NET Framework 4 Client Profile. .NET Framework 4 Client Profile is a subset of .NET Framework 4. The vulnerability addressed in this update affects both .NET Framework 4 and .NET Framework 4 Client Profile. For more information, see the MSDN article, [Installing the .NET Framework](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5a4x27ek).
<p><sup>[2]</sup>This update is available via <a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=21130" data-linktype="external">Windows Update</a>.</p>
